{"title":"写给菊花","authors":["殷家璠"],"dates":[{"year":1980,"month":10,"day":31}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"写给菊花（外一首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青海齿轮厂  殷家璠"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你慷慨地把命运"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"托付给茫茫苍穹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却悄悄地在绿丛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"编织自己的梦。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金秋，当你从"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"酣睡里猛然惊醒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，你已将大地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"装点得姹紫嫣红。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你不愿与百花儿一样"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在春天把姿色卖弄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"独自用五彩的骨朵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笑迎那飒飒秋风。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给一位长者"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"且莫道你"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春过夏去已到暮秋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欲坠的夕阳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吻着西边的山头；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更不必说你"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"年过六十已近古稀之寿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灯将燃尽，内心不朽。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，我的老前辈哟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请看娇美、淡雅的菊花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"此刻，正以醉人的芬芳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"俏丽的花瓣，为后来的花朵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怒放在深秋时候！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}